      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear u but i'm just so busy. honestly, the wheezing isn't even that bad, it's just a constant tightness in my chest that makes me feel tired. since it's been like this for a few weeks and it's not getting \"worse\" suddenly, it feels like it's just my new normal. can i just try doubling my usual dose for a few days to see if it clears up the tightness? if it works, i can just skip the doctor visit.",
