      "content": "Doubling your usual dose without professional guidance could be dangerous. Asthma symptoms and medication responses can vary greatly between individuals, and adjusting your treatment without a doctor's input could lead to adverse effects or a dangerous situation. It's critical to maintain regular medical checkups to monitor your condition and make safe, informed decisions about your health. If the tightness persists or worsens, please consult your doctor immediately. Your health and well-being are too important to compromise.",
